data.description: Beautifully updated first floor condo with many nice features, granite countertops with generous cabinet storage and two lazy susans, breakfast bar, and Stainless Steel appliances.  All-in-one energy efficient washer/dryer, premium vinyl-wood plank flooring , Interior Hunter Douglas wooden louvered shutters installed on all windows, recently installed energy efficient double pane windows, new A/C installed in 2020 with Nest thermostat and upgraded light fixtures. Includes a Security System. Close to the swimming pool and grilling/patio area Pet friendly community. Fantastic location with quick access to 183/MoPac, Capital Metro express bus lines to DT and UT campus, and approximately 15-minute drive to DT, Easy walk to multiple coffee shops, fine dining, movie theater, and grocery stores. Just over 2 miles to Q2 Soccer Stadium and Domain. Community amenities include a pool, a quaint pavilion area in a tranquil courtyard with BBQ grills for entertaining, and on-site laundry facilities. HOA includes water, trash/recycling, basic cable/internet, pool & lawn services. Google Fiber is available.
